=Description=

"Novaglobe was established in 2009 as a global variant of the New Netherlands movement in Holland. This movement was initiated by the vision an feeling that the nowadays 'system', our ecosystem is halted. It is jammed. Systemjam. And the various eco subsystems (politics, monetary sector, justice, etc.), are not able to create the desired fundamental change. Watch the Zeitgeist movie. Read the books of Ervin Laszlo. So, we, the people, the citizins will do it ourselves. Why not?"



